# SocialCredit Addons

This repository acts as the public index for addons built for the SocialCredit core framework.

## Official Addons

Official addons are maintained by the SocialCredit project and are considered part of the supported ecosystem.

- SocialCreditExampleAddon — reference addon demonstrating API/event usage
- SocialCreditBlackMarket — extended illegal trade / state pressure gameplay

## Community Addons

Community addons are built independently. These are not maintained by the core project unless explicitly stated.

- ExampleCommunityAddon — demonstrates custom penalty policy hooks

## Listing Rules

To be listed here, addons should:
- target the public SocialCredit API
- avoid internal classes and direct DB access
- clearly state supported core version(s)
- include source or clear release information

## Support Boundary

Official addons are supported as part of the SocialCredit ecosystem.

Community addons are listed for visibility only unless otherwise stated.
